{"parents": [{"link": "../../", "title": "Guides"}], "prev": {"link": "../../", "title": "Guides"}, "next": {"link": "../create_a_store/", "title": "Stores: Creating a Store"}, "title": "Stores: Managing a Store", "meta": null, "body": "<div class=\"section\" id=\"stores-managing-a-store\">\n<h1>Stores: Managing a Store<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#stores-managing-a-store\" title=\"Permalink to this headline\">\u00b6</a></h1>\n<div class=\"line-block\">\n<div class=\"line\">Among the many features of the Maha Platform, an important one is the facilitation of engagement in e-commerce.</div>\n<div class=\"line\">It does so by allowing you to create online storefronts to sell your products.</div>\n<div class=\"line\">Refer to <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"/users/guides/stores/create_a_store.html\">Creating a Store</a> to create a new store.</div>\n</div>\n<ol class=\"arabic simple\">\n<li><p>Click the <i class=\"fa fa-bars\"></i> in the ribbon</p></li>\n<li><p>Click <strong>Stores</strong></p></li>\n<li><p>Click <i class=\"fa fa-ellipsis-h\"></i> and <strong>Edit Store</strong> to <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"/users/general/guides/functions_of_the_grid/how_to_edit.html\">edit</a> the store</p></li>\n<li><p>Click <i class=\"fa fa-ellipsis-h\"></i> and <strong>Clone Store</strong></p>\n<ul class=\"simple\">\n<li><p><a class=\"reference external\" href=\"/users/general/guides/functions_of_the_grid/how_to_edit.html\">Edit</a> the store if desired and then click <strong>Clone</strong></p></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><p>Click <i class=\"fa fa-ellipsis-h\"></i>, click <strong>Delete Store</strong>, and click <strong>Yes</strong> to delete the store</p></li>\n<li><p>Click a store to view and interact with the following features: <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"/users/guides/stores/details.html\">Details</a>, <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"/users/guides/stores/categories.html\">Categories</a>, <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"/users/guides/stores/products.html\">Products</a>, <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"/users/guides/stores/fields.html\">Fields</a>, <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"/users/guides/stores/inventory.html\">Inventory</a>, <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"/users/guides/stores/automation.html\">Automation</a>, <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"/users/guides/stores/campaigns.html\">Campaigns</a>, <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"/users/guides/stores/carts.html\">Carts</a>, <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"/users/guides/stores/orders.html\">Orders</a>, <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"/users/guides/stores/fulfillment.html\">Fulfillment</a>, <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"/users/guides/stores/performance.html\">Performance</a></p></li>\n</ol>\n</div>\n", "metatags": "", "rellinks": [["genindex", "General Index", "I", "index"], ["users/stores/guides/create_a_store", "Stores: Creating a Store", "N", "next"], ["users/stores/index", "Guides", "P", "previous"]], "sourcename": "users/stores/guides/stores.rst.txt", "toc": "<ul>\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#\">Stores: Managing a Store</a></li>\n</ul>\n", "display_toc": false, "page_source_suffix": ".rst", "current_page_name": "users/stores/guides/stores", "sidebars": ["localtoc.html", "relations.html", "sourcelink.html", "searchbox.html"], "customsidebar": null, "favicon_url": null, "logo_url": null, "alabaster_version": "0.7.12"}